<p>
Jarmo Halonen is the founder of ProfitAndPrivilege.com, where he researches affiliate marketing, online business opportunities, AI tools, and digital entrepreneurship.
</p>

<p>
Originally from Finland and now based in Sweden, Jarmo combines more than 30 years of experience in network marketing with a background as a tanker truck driver transporting industrial chemicals. His career has taught him the value of long-term relationship building, consistency, and practical business development.
</p>

<p>
His long experience with <a href="https://bestbuybounty.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">NeoLife</a> has provided practical insight into relationship-based network marketing and sustainable business building. His editorial focus also includes <a href="https://olspacademy.com/megalive/1006001" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer sponsored">OLSP Academy</a>, whose affiliate marketing education and two-tier commission structure reflect many of the long-term business principles he values.
</p>

<p>
Through ProfitAndPrivilege, Jarmo publishes evidence-based reviews, comparison guides, and educational content. His editorial approach distinguishes verified facts, vendor claims, and community opinions, helping readers make informed decisions before investing their time or money.
</p>

